title: Doing Business in Deep Waters

description:
In this message, Joel will explain that whenever you do something great for God or "do business in deep waters" you will face attacks. It's very easy to get discouraged. Instead give your battles to God and let Him fight for you.----Visit https://joelosteen.com to receive daily updates and encouragement from Joel Osteen.----Have you followed Joel Osteen on Instagram? https://instagram.com/joelosteen.
